items.name: Quirky Space Bar, Assorted Colors
items.shortDescription: Space Bar is a sleek desk accessory that minimizes clutter while providing additional USB ports for your computer. After a long day of work, slide your keyboard into the space below the shelf and store your office miscellany — keys, digital camera, etc. It can stow a keyboard up to 18 inches by 1.5 inches, has room up to store small items and supports up to 30.5 pounds (a 27-inch Apple iMac). It's got six USB ports: four in the front that charge and sync and two that charge in the rear. It also includes one miniUSB port and one AC adapter port. Space Bar is simple and elegantly designed. It's made from shiny-brushed aluminum with Apple-esque white accents.
